\id 2JN - Kanasi NT [soq] -Papua New Guinea 1996 (DBL 2014) 
\h 2 Ion 
\toc1 2 Ion Ion letawa natawa ekelesia dea mampo girumalena 
\toc2 2 Ion 
\mt1 2 Ion  
\mt2 Ion letawa natawa ekelesia dea mampo girumalena  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Ne Ion ekelesia onionia apanawa letana ema e i sonabalala obana do manlawo girumantedina. E ne do ulaipa gagalowa bedewe deantene wainitana baiwa nuawadawadaledina. Tane mai ne os, sumanailala mo mida ulaipa intawa dauwa etane atentoiena do nuawadawadaleie auwalei!   
\p
\v 2 No nuawadawada mampe auwaleitana, ipawa ulaipa aiawa no bedemboido winedie inileide ita no mainimbo winakasalempa ideita walama ompe.  
\v 3 God no Mamamba ita me Otopa Iesu Keriso nuawadawadau amonawa, nuapareu no baimba, ita do nuaeu nenompo wainenta. God sauwa eubu ema ulaipa gagalowa ita nuawadawada bedeuwoe no nenompa.   
\s1 Ulaipa waeuwa ita nuawadawada bedewe wainenta!  
\p
\v 4 Ne nuana eudidalen, ipawa ne donsana e obana sumanailala isiwa ulaipa waeuwa ruawantoie waimoi, Mamamba anaana nenena wadia rua.  
\v 5 \x + \xo 1.5 \xt Ion 13.34; 15.12,17\x*Tane tauma i sonabalala dieedina no eda nuawadawadantipona. Ne mai anaana sanaa girumanteipona e manawo, dia. Tane ema ipa bumpeido no mainimbo winedia deawaa wadine nuala itudina.  
\v 6 \bd Ita nuawadawada ipawaida ipa ema epe: No God anaanawa etatana ruawantata. Me anaanawa e uduudu bumpeido etalana ipa ema epe: E nuawadawada bedewe wanlempa.\bd*   
\p
\v 7 Ne aia ema wadina, ipawa laga apanawa uara nomone tawo uduudu bedewe antontuwan. Mo waeuwantoie waiase, “Iesu Keriso tawo osowe wisene mai apanaida etemba wadape no ruambalepona, dia.” Apana dainea epe wadia, me ipa lagawaaida ita Keriso onawaida apanawa.  
\v 8 Sa baiwa e sumanailala ewanadewaitana dima no e bedelawo nolawantena mai rebasana, tane e ideita unela nopelala wadana.   
\p
\v 9 Apana mida Keriso waeuwa ulaipa bedewe wandie tane edie ulaipa waeuwa andiboe waeuwa da sanaa lagawaa asiasi aleidia, me ipa mai God do, dia. \bd Tane mida Keriso waeuwa ulaipa bedewe wankasaleidia, me mampe Mamamba ita Otopa do waimoi.\bd*  
\v 10 Naita apana mida e manlawo wisepie waeuwalepie wapiase, “Keriso tawo ema osowe wisene mai apanaida etemba wadape no ruambalepona,” e apana sa mai nuaeusana ba banleno dulawo odepi, ena.  
\v 11 Tane mida apana sa auwasapia me nolawa kadiwa sa do bedewelepi.   
\p
\v 12 Ne gagalo uaraia mainawo wineia girumanteapona e manlawo, tane ne mai girumanteapa, dia. Tane ne insedina ibunaida e manlawo wineape e do gagalontate ita nuaeu nuamba nopeidosapi.   
\p
\v 13 E tataa sonabalala obampa e auwaa waiaubei.  
\p Ne letana kampaida mape dialen, niapo!   